               "CAC 40","MOEX","OMXS 30","Oslo Bors All-Share","TSX","IBOVESPA","IPC Mexico","SHANGHAI 50",

for i in range(len(Countries)):
    data = yf.download(Yahoo_indeces[i], start="2020-01-02", end=str(today.date()))
    stock_hist=pd.DataFrame(data[['Close','Volume']])
    stock_hist['Country']=Countries[i]
    stock_hist['Index Name']=Stock_indeces[i]
    if i == 0:
        stock_history=stock_hist
    else:
        stock_history=pd.concat([stock_history,stock_hist])

stock_history.to_csv('stock_indeces.csv')
